description:
This is the full moon of 26 May 2021 behind the Q1 building in Surfers Paradise - the tallest building in Australia.
A group of waving SkyPoint climbers can be seen silhouetted against the moon  (I was in communication with the climb instructor via phone & relayed two-way radio)

This is a still frame taken from a video of the event, recorded in "5K"  RAW format using Sharpcap Pro - the .SER format video was 96 gigabytes in size.
I used a ZWO ASI183 MC Pro camera and Sigma 120-300mm F/2.8 Sports lens and 1.4x teleconverter

The video can be seen here - as well a a second one using a 952mm refractor and ZWO ASI 294MC-Pro

https://vimeo.com/555510912
Instagram : @phasefourphoto
title: SkyPoint Climbers Silhouetted against the Full Moon
